    "description": "cr4ckr is a puzzle game about cracking passwords.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nPiece together the missing components of the password using the hint letters provided and the clues from the surrounding words. You'll only have access to the first and last components. Guess correctly, and the next piece of the puzzle is revealed. But be warned—time is running out! As you race to crack the code, the police are hot on your trail, tracing your connection with every passing second.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nCan you outsmart the system and crack the password before the trace is complete? Or will the authorities catch up with you, ending your hacking spree once and for all? Only the sharpest minds will prevail in this game of speed, strategy, and wordplay.",
